    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against required level 3; this shortfall is accepted based on ASTM F1717 protocol constraints and regulatory precedent. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). FEA model credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
